erate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/140948/', '', 'Danazol, Ospemifene, Raloxifene, Bazedoxifene, Prasterone', 'Hemin, Conestat alfa, Betibeglogene autotemcel, Hyaluronidase, Streptokinase, Human C1-esterase inhibitor, Crizanlizumab, Lanadelumab, Icatibant', 1767369485);
